headline: Will Hologic (HOLX) Beat Estimates Again in Its Next Earnings Report?
summary: Hologic (HOLX) has an impressive earnings surprise history and currently possesses the right combination of the two key ingredients for a likely beat in its next quarterly report.

headline: Will GYN Surgical Power Hologic's Growth in the Upcoming Q1 Earnings?
summary: HOLX's GYN Surgical unit, boosted by MyoSure, Fluent and Gynesonics, drives 10.2% revenue growth and is likely to lift upcoming Q1 results.
